.DT
set_monitor
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_monitor

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_monitor -  Set the hit point monitor.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_monitor(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new value for the hit point monitor flag

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Set the hit point monitor.  This sets the value of the hit point
monitor flag.  If it is set to 0, the monitor is turned off.  If
it is set to 1 the monitor is turned on.
.EP

